# Heimdall k3s control plane — example env file.
#
# Authoritative source: Heimdall/secrets/k3s-control-plane.sops.env (SOPS+age).
# Decrypted by Heimdall/scripts/deploy.sh on the workstation, then shipped to
# /opt/Homelab/Heimdall/k3s-control-plane/.env on Heimdall (.gitignored, 0600).
#
# The same K3S_TOKEN value must also be present in
# Hyperion/nixos/secrets/common.yaml as k3s-token: (encrypted to the operator
# + every per-node USB age key). See README.md §"Initial mint".

# Pre-shared join token. 32 bytes of hex (64 chars) is the conventional size.
K3S_TOKEN=replace-with-64-hex-chars
